            "answer_text": "If you woke up in the middle of a dream, does it mean you woke up during a deep sleep? Quite the contrary. If you were dreaming it means that you were nearly awake. Dreams occur during REM sleep\u2014which is about as close to being awake as you can get without being awake. Your conscious is aware of what is going on in your brain\u2014random images that your consciousness interprets as a narrative. You do not dream at all during the deepest cycle of sleep when everything is almost completely shut down. ",
